<HEADLINE>
<P>
HIGH SCHOOL BASKETBALL ROUNDUP; 
</P>
<P>
POWAY GIRLS BEAT VISTA, STAY PERFECT IN LEAGUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Dawn Gigstad led a balanced attack with 10 points as Poway improved to 4-0 in 
the Palomar League with a 60-37 girls' basketball victory over Vista Thursday 
at Poway. 
</P>
<P>
The Titans (12-1) also had four players with eight points apiece. 
</P>
<P>
