<P>
Photo, Controversial road twists upward into hills and Ramirez Canyon above 
Malibu beachfront area. CASSY COHEN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Developer 
Charles Tarrats holds Bible in hands at meeting of Coastal Commission. LISA 
ROMEREIN / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
