<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Sandbox Memories: Dennis Dickman of Van Nuys plays with daughter Jenna, 
2 1/2, at Van Nuys-Sherman Oaks Park. MEL MELCON 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
