<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, This untitled artwork is among the sculpture and drawings of Darrell 
Burdette being featured through Feb. 3 at Gallery 57 in Fullerton. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
