<TEXT>
<P>
An explosive device, apparently a simulated military grenade, detonated outside 
a state government building this morning, a day after incendiary devices were 
found in San Francisco and Palo Alto Macy's and Sak's Fifth Avenue department 
stores, police said. 
</P>
<P>
